content: I've been thinking about my business's financials, and I realized that I've been doing okay so far, considering I've only been in business for a few months. It's crazy to think that it's already been three months since I started considering starting my own business - it feels like just yesterday I was attending that entrepreneurship seminar that inspired me to take the leap. Anyway, back to my financials... do you have any advice on how to determine my pricing strategy for my writing services?
